canPass

public boolean canPass()
Evaluates if the player can pass through this cell. The player can pass through this cell only if it can also pass through the adyacent cell of the destiny, moving in the same direction as when it entered this cell.

Specified by:
canPass in class Cell
Returns:
True if it can. False if it can not
